{"tid":1712731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 可唔可以爭氣一次","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T15:19:42.000Z","uid":192304,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dea8862d300c54227d0e429f37e1cf43dacd8f2d","tid":1712731,"uid":192304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"中大今日搞到咁 仲有好多人淨係識得repost新聞 發放負能量<br />\n呢個時候先做所謂嘅文宣已經無效<br />\n大家可唔可以做實事 爭氣少少 聽朝早起多一次 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一齊塞爆黨鐵 塞爆條街 <br />\n等罷唔到工、罷唔到課嘅香港人一齊被罷 <br />\n有能力罷到嘅就唔好再比藉口自己 罷左佢！！</strong><br />\n</span><br />\n求下你地 再唔做 恐怕以後無得再做<br />\n好多手足入哂廠 入狗屋 無屋企返 <span style=\"color: violet;\">最細得11歲</span><br />\n 你係咪仲坐起到咩都唔做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fsn8K3j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsn8K3j.png&h=f561b9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利申：學生妹已經孤身作戰 罷左2日課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05edbb804b95042c0ddc7b273cce4c3c7828c170","tid":1712731,"uid":192304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫手推"},{"pid":"a8aad9e413eec40ff5ba9abb41cf81f922e06733","tid":1712731,"uid":192304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.g